	<div class="box-content">
		<p><strong>Language</strong><br />English is preferred but you can write in any language. Automated translation to over 50 languages is offered via Google translator.</p> 
		<p><strong>Headline</strong><br />Grabâ€™s attention, summarize the whole thought and attracts to read the rest of the story.</p>
