		<p><strong>The threat and opportunity</strong><br />Identify the most important threat and opportunity if vision is realized.</p>
		<p><strong>Keywords</strong><br />Words that capture the essence of the topic of your content. Are important, since we use them for related content automatization.</p> 
		<p><strong>Related companies and organizations</strong><br/>Similar as keywords but present existing companies and organizations, which are related to your insight.</p> 
